{
    "info": {
        "_postman_id": "authmaster-api-v5",
        "name": "AuthMaster API",
        "description": "# AuthMaster API Collection\n\nComplete API collection for the Redoy/AuthMaster Laravel Package.\n\n## ðŸ”’ Secure Registration Flow (Verify Before Create)\nTo prevent unauthorized email usage, this package implements a **Pending Registration** flow:\n\n1. **Register**: User submits details. System validates but **does NOT create the account** yet.\n   - Stores data in secure cache.\n   - Sends OTP or Link to email.\n   - Returns `pending_registration: true`.\n\n2. **Verify**: User submits OTP or clicks Link.\n   - System validates token.\n   - **Creates user account**.\n   - Logs user in and returns access token.\n\n## ðŸ“§ Verification Methods\n- **OTP**: Standard 6-digit code (Dev Default: `123456`).\n- **Link**: Secure verification link (e.g., `/verify-email?token=...`).\n\n## ðŸš€ Getting Started\n1. Import this collection.\n2. Set validation method in your Laravel config (`link` or `otp`).\n3. Use **Registration Flow** folder to test.\n4. Copy `token` from verify response to test protected routes.",
        "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
    },
    "item": [
        {
            "name": "Registration Flow",
            "description": "Step-by-step secure registration process",
            "item": [
                {
                    "name": "1. Register (Start)",
                    "event": [
                        {
                            "listen": "test",
                            "script": {
                                "exec": [
                                    "pm.test('Status code is 200', function () {",
                                    "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                                    "});",
                                    "",
                                    "pm.test('Pending registration', function () {",
                                    "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                                    "    pm.expect(jsonData.data.pending_registration).to.eql(true);",
                                    "    ",
                                    "    // Save dev tokens if returned",
                                    "    if (jsonData.data.dev_token) {",
                                    "        pm.collectionVariables.set('link_token', jsonData.data.dev_token);",
                                    "    }",
                                    "});"
                                ],
                                "type": "text/javascript"
                            }
                        }
                    ],
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Accept",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            },
                            {
                                "key": "Content-Type",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n    \"name\": \"{{test_name}}\",\n    \"email\": \"{{test_email}}\",\n    \"password\": \"{{test_password}}\",\n    \"password_confirmation\": \"{{test_password}}\"\n}"
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/register",
                            "host": [
                                "{{base_url}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "auth",
                                "register"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "### Step 1: Submit Registration\n\nInitiates the registration process.\n\n**Behavior:**\n- Validates input.\n- Checks if email is already taken (by verified user).\n- **Stores pending data** temporarily.\n- Sends verification email (OTP or Link based on config).\n\n**Response:**\n- `pending_registration`: `true`\n- `email_verification_required`: `true`"
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "2a. Verify Email (OTP Mode)",
                    "event": [
                        {
                            "listen": "test",
                            "script": {
                                "exec": [
                                    "pm.test('Status code is 201', function () {",
                                    "    pm.response.to.have.status(201);",
                                    "});",
                                    "",
                                    "pm.test('Account created and token returned', function () {",
                                    "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                                    "    pm.expect(jsonData.success).to.eql(true);",
                                    "    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('token');",
                                    "});",
                                    "",
                                    "pm.test('Save token', function () {",
                                    "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                                    "    var tokenData = jsonData.data ? jsonData.data.token : null;",
                                    "    var token = null;",
                                    "    if (tokenData) {",
                                    "        token = (typeof tokenData.access_token === 'string') ? tokenData.access_token : (tokenData.token || tokenData.access_token);",
                                    "    }",
                                    "    if (token) {",
                                    "        pm.collectionVariables.set('token', token);",
                                    "    }",
                                    "});"
                                ],
                                "type": "text/javascript"
                            }
                        }
                    ],
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Accept",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            },
                            {
                                "key": "Content-Type",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n    \"email\": \"{{test_email}}\",\n    \"code\": \"{{otp_code}}\"\n}"
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/verify-email",
                            "host": [
                                "{{base_url}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "auth",
                                "verify-email"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "### Step 2a: Complete Registration (OTP)\n\nUse this if `email_verification` is set to `otp`.\n\n**Params:**\n- `email`: Required to find pending registration.\n- `code`: The OTP code received.\n\n**Dev OTP:** `123456`"
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "2b. Verify Email (Link Mode - POST)",
                    "event": [
                        {
                            "listen": "test",
                            "script": {
                                "exec": [
                                    "pm.test('Status code is 201', function () {",
                                    "    pm.response.to.have.status(201);",
                                    "});",
                                    "",
                                    "pm.test('Account created and token returned', function () {",
                                    "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                                    "    pm.expect(jsonData.success).to.eql(true);",
                                    "    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('token');",
                                    "});",
                                    "",
                                    "pm.test('Save token', function () {",
                                    "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                                    "    var token = (jsonData.data && jsonData.data.token) ? (jsonData.data.token.access_token || jsonData.data.token.token) : null;",
                                    "    if (token) {",
                                    "        pm.collectionVariables.set('token', token);",
                                    "    }",
                                    "});"
                                ],
                                "type": "text/javascript"
                            }
                        }
                    ],
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Accept",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            },
                            {
                                "key": "Content-Type",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n    \"token\": \"{{link_token}}\"\n}"
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/verify-email",
                            "host": [
                                "{{base_url}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "auth",
                                "verify-email"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "### Step 2b: Complete Registration (Link - POST)\n\nSimulates verification via POST request.\n\n**Params:**\n- `token`: The token string.\n\n**Dev Token:** `dev-verification-token`"
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "2c. Verify Email (Browser Link - GET)",
                    "event": [
                        {
                            "listen": "test",
                            "script": {
                                "exec": [
                                    "pm.test('Status code is 201 or 200', function () {",
                                    "    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.be.oneOf([200, 201]);",
                                    "});"
                                ],
                                "type": "text/javascript"
                            }
                        }
                    ],
                    "request": {
                        "method": "GET",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Accept",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            }
                        ],
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/verify-email?token={{link_token}}",
                            "host": [
                                "{{base_url}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "auth",
                                "verify-email"
                            ],
                            "query": [
                                {
                                    "key": "token",
                                    "value": "{{link_token}}"
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "### Step 2c: Complete Registration (Link - Browser GET)\n\nSimulates a browser click on the verification link.\n\n**Params:**\n- `token`: Query parameter.\n\n**Dev Token:** `dev-verification-token`"
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
